{
  "stem": "3605.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember when I was already 13 years old, I used to go to school, and there was a poor woman sitting there in front of the school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I gave her my lunch before I even walked in to the school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somebody told it to my mother, so later on, they used to send the maid to school, and I had to eat in the teachers' room with my--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somehow, even during the war, I need to bring out, my mind wasn't so around food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my body maybe didn't need so much food as other people needed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I-- the war kept going on and during the camps that I lived in, I never at up my piece of bread till I did not get another piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, 'I have bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just don't want to eat it.' And that didn't made me so wild hungry, because people were so hungry, like worse than any animal you can-- hungry animal you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How did you take care of your garden of vegetables?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I say, the garden of vegetables just wasn't my garden.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the group's.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was distributed strictly between our sick members.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the night was a curfew, and nobody could go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during the day, we were around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And besides, the group of the people that were there were, I have to say, honorable young people with ideals.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with-- and it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There wasn't so much for everybody to go around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was mainly to prolong the life of those that were weak and those that were sick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was mainly used for that purpose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There wasn't so much of it either.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
